{"tid":2099320,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有時踎低搬野，起身個下大脾會抽搐一下","createTime":"2020-07-08T06:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T07:45:15.000Z","uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b89091ebaf85335b14c7b293ef28b344617a33","tid":2099320,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"普通做踎低起身運動又唔會有，但係最近踎低拎重野起身個下我大脾內側會抽搐一下，唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細佬做物流，好著重搬野姿勢，所以本身都冇咩勞損腰痛，因為但係最近就發現會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca165f3e7e2ab21279055846d9af599caab408d","tid":2099320,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"<del>因為</del>"},{"pid":"2dd3e9385d3f98be17b97d3216578373046c9eaf","tid":2099320,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"鳩根都縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab009b15d0d9a11dbf2f0678bd906180cf4ab24","tid":2099320,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:58:55.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n又唔係下下搬重野都會抽，可能係間唔中搬五六野抽一野咁"},{"pid":"57e1a713658faab1878d0724ffa776133f75d35e","tid":2099320,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:02:53.000Z","msg":"我有個frd 又係咁,佢打籃球, <br />\n有次佢復出之後打打下, 睇住佢腳眼拉到到上小腿果條根, 突然好似橡筋咁一野扯斷左<br />\n最後抖左1 年行唔到"},{"pid":"a1f53ca95d21bda35e9e1b009329173583b020b3","tid":2099320,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"會唔會係大脾內側上少少再上少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f9696b63fe9f3b18144a2d5c0ed679a75877e4","tid":2099320,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e1a713658faab1878d0724ffa776133f75d35e","tid":2099320,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit